TextEng: The same to you, Sir William. Farewell.
Yes, well, I had best be going then...
This ending comes at a price, Sir William...
Text: 이 결말에는 대가가 따르는군요, 윌리엄 경...

TextEng: It warms the heart to see true love blossom.
Text: 진정한 사랑이 꽃피는 걸 보니 마음이 따뜻해지는군.

TextEng: So all's well that ends well?
Do not concern yourself with it, Sir William.
It is already mine, my friend.
Do you know how to find the Wise Wind?
What happened? How can I help?
Can you not charge to her rescue?
Who is this Jendra you weep for?
Calm down, eveything's going to be okay...
